# Welcome to ZeroWiki

[[ZeroWiki]] is a new kind of publishing platform for [[ZeroNet]], the distributed web network based on Bittorrent and [[Bitcoin]].

ZeroWiki is public [[wiki]] software, and most of the pages in this site are editable. Anyone can modify, adding or improving content. See the [help page](http://127.0.0.1:43110/138R53t3ZW7KDfSfxVpWUsMXgwUnsDNXLP/?Help) to learn how it works.

Wikis can be used for taking notes, storing snippets, creating [[FAQ]]s and documentation, keeping track of your goals, or as a simple to-do list. 

Use it however you want! ZeroWiki is free and cloneable from your ZeroNet connected sites.

## [[List of Zites]]

## Testing

For testing please use the [[ZeroWiki:Sandbox]].

## ZeroWiki is beta software

This project is still in beta phase and it may have bugs or lack features.

Please report bugs and add feature requests to the [[ZeroWiki:Issues]] page.

# Welcome to ZeroWiki

[[ZeroWiki]] is a new kind of **publishing platform for [[ZeroNet]]**, the distributed web network based on Bittorrent and [[Bitcoin]].

ZeroWiki is a public [[wiki]] software and most of the pages in this site are editable, anyone can modify it to add or improve the contents. See the [help page](http://127.0.0.1:43110/138R53t3ZW7KDfSfxVpWUsMXgwUnsDNXLP/?Help) to learn how it works.

Wikis can be used for taking notes and storing snippets, creating [[FAQs|FAQ]]s and documentation, keeping track of your goals, or as a simple to-do list. 

Use it however you want! ZeroWiki is free and cloneable from your ZeroNet connected sites.
